captions.text: Why standing?
What do you mean why standing?
Why are you standing here?

Do you know that it's the sidewalk?
-Huh?
Do you know that it's the sidewalk?
There are cars standing here, why you don't tell them anything? I'm going to Rosgosstrakh for example
What should we say to cars?

We don't talk to inanimate objects
-So well
But you're a human, a driver that is moving along the sidewalk
I'm going to Rosgosstrakh, I need to get to Rosgosstrakh
Use the road

So what?
-What do you mean so what?
Where's any "No thoroughfare" sign out here?

Do you even know the Traffic Code? You're moving along the sidewalk
-I do know
Is there any "sidewalk" sign out here?

What do you mean a "sidewalk" sign? Have you ever seen the Traffic Code? 
-What do you need from me?
What do you mean what we need? It's the sidewalk, people walk here
What are you doing?
If you run over, we will put a sticker on your windscreen. Don't run over people
Get out of my way, I have to get to Rosgosstrakh
We won't move, get back on the road, nobody will leave this spot. This is the sidewalk

So what?
-Nothing!
Move away, I'm telling you, I have to get to Rosgosstrakh
Nobody will move
Man, don't run over people
If you run over we will put a sticker on your windscreen
So what? I put it off
You won't be able, it will stuck
Come on, get out of here, what do you think you're doing?
Nobody will move, don't run over people. Don't push these people
You're on the sidewalk

Man, don't run over people please
-What?
Don't run over people
I'm not running over, just move away
Nobody will move away, they're standing on the sidewalk

Man, they won't move away anyway
-What sidewalk?
This sidewalk where people walk
Come on, stop doing this crap
We're not doing crap man
We're asking you to back out and get back on the road please

What?
-Get back on the road man
Just move away
They won't move
Could you please back out so that they could pass?
Hello, there's the road near here, this is the sidewalk
I have my own store right here, i'm going there

You have your own store right there?
-Yes, grocery store 24/7
I understand, there's an entry to your store over there
That is my wife. What's your problem I don't understand?
No problem, look, there's the road
I know but I'm going to my store. You don't understand Russian?
We do understand Russian

You have nothing to do or what?
-Yes
Good
What are you doing?
If you're gonna touch people we will put a sticker on your windscreen
I'm going to my store
I'm trying to tell you, please use the road

I will park over there
-People walk here
Do you even hear me?
All people drive on the road, this is the sidewalk, there are people walking here
To the right to the clinic
There's a passage to the clinic right there, the jam isn't that big
I understand that to the clinic. But use the road, not sidewalks

Not sidewalks?
-Yes. This is the sidewalk
Thanks for understanding

Guys get your camera away

I gotta do it myself then. Get the camera away!

Hello, you can film me
Well, show me your ID

Because I am a policeman
Show me your ID then

She has a right to film you
I have a right to film her too
